amming, or is it a genetic profile?<br /><br /><i><b>A: Hatred of humanity due to early infant programming</b></i><br /><br />Q: (Joe) I.e. involving circumcision...<br /><br />A: Yes.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />That said by the C&#039;s I now understand some things. And one of those things is the case of the current president of Argentina, Javier Milei, and his association with the Lubavitch sect.<br /><br />The question here is that since I have been examining the how and why of Javier Milei&#039;s career and his rise to the presidency, it is now clear to me (and until now it was an assumption that I did not dare to comment on because of the seriousness of the matter) that Milei shares this same hatred for humanity. Not only because of his last statements about how the Argentine people have to suffer. From Milei it is known that he was very angry with his parents, from the alleged incestuous relationship with his sister, from the unfortunate comments about free sale of organs and comments like <a href=\"https://www-elpatagonico-com.translate.goog/los-preocupantes-ejemplos-milei-ninos-envaselinados-pedofilos-y-violaciones-n5847899?_x_tr_sl=auto&amp;_x_tr_tl=es&amp;_x_tr_hl=es&amp;_x_tr_pto=wapp\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\"><i>naked children in Vaseline</i></a>. And his obsessive love for his dogs (emotional support).<br /><br />All this makes me think that Milei, as a child, went through a traumatic event in which his parents turned a blind eye. Use your imagination...","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17664,"user":"Pluchi","date":"2024-02-15T18:32:36+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":13931,"user":"OutSky","date":"2024-01-29T19:33:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-24T03:46:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17316,"user":"KaWaiAwaAwa","date":"2024