 unavailable.<br /><br /><div class=\"bbCodeSpoiler\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-button button--longText button\" data-xf-click=\"toggle\" data-xf-init=\"tooltip\" title=\"Click to reveal or hide spoiler\"><span class=\"button-text\"><span>Spoiler: <span class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-button-title\">Russian spelling</span></span></span></button><div class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--spoiler\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\">Возможно, но у нас наблюдается обратная картина. Был один сайт, на котором было много материала , переведенного на русский. Почти все до 2018 года. Похоже, что в том году они остановили работу, но сайт был доступен, можно было почитать и  вот уже некоторое время, по неизвестной причине этот сайт недоступен.</div></div></div></div>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T17:57:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6869,"user":"artofdream","date":"2024-01-21T05:37:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T00:52:27+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:41:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15344,"user":"Cassis","date":"2024-01-19T19:14:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-19T18:54:55+0100","reaction":"Sad"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-19T05:18:06+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10151,"user":"pinkfreud","date":"2024-01-18T18:21:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11107,"user":"kaixin82","date":"2024-01-18T00:44:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-17T23:32:13+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":118,"user":"annp","date":"2024-01-17T20:58:02+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12341,"user":"Laurentien2","date":"2024-01-17T18:56:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4845,"user":"naorma","date":"2024-01-17T17:14:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay