47,"user":"unkl brws","date":"2024-01-16T18:00:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14216,"user":"f1esk","date":"2024-01-16T17:24:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-01-16T17:22:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4518,"user":"Adobe","date":"2024-01-16T17:20:50+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":14216,"user":"f1esk","id":1155686,"date":"2024-01-16T17:22:31+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 9769\" data-quote=\"Altair\" data-source=\"post: 1155679\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155679\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155679\">Altair said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">You probably mean the <a href=\"http://dreamland-exit.info\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Dreamland</a> website. They had unofficial Google translations of bad quality, and we have nothing to do with them. Besides, their website is closed since several years.<br /><br />Actually, we have already <b>tons of material</b> translated into Russian:<br /><ul><li data-xf-list-type=\"ul\"><a href=\"https://www.pilulerouge.com/ru/product-category/books-ru/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">several translated books</a></li><li data-xf-list-type=\"ul\"><i>Wave</i> 1-3, partly <i>Wave</i> 4 (new translated chapters are still being added) and <i>High Strangeness</i> available <a href=\"https://ru.cassiopaea.org\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">online to read</a></li><li data-xf-list-type=\"ul\"><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/boards/russian.88/\" class=\"link link--internal\">sessions translated into Russian</a> (from 2021 ongoing)</li><li data-xf-list-type=\"ul\">our <a href=\"https://x-ufo.ru\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">blog</a> in Russian dedicated to UFOs and High Strangeness. All the translations from <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.substack.com\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Cassiopaea Substack</a> and much more go there.</li><li data-xf-list-type=\"ul\">Russian-speaking <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/boards/russkij.84/\" class=\"link link--internal\">section of the forum</a></li><li data-xf-list-type=\"ul\"><a href=\"https://ru.sott.net\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">ru.sott.net</a> with lots of translated materials as well. For example,<a href=\"https://ru.sott.net/topic/31-zemnye-izmeneniya-i-vzaimosvyaz-mezhdu-chelovekom-i-kosmosom\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\"> all the chapters</a> from the Pierre&#039;s <i>Earth Changes</i> book, <a href=\"https://ru.sott.net/topic/36-massovye-vymiraniya-evolyutsionnye-skachki-i-svyaz-virusovs-informatsiey\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">all the chapters</a> from Pierre&#039;s unpublished <i>Mass Extinctions</i> book.</li></ul></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Or we are talking about the site <b>omartasatt.ru</b>, it was there in 2009-2011 that I first learned about Cassiapeia. There were translations of &quot;The Wave&quot;. Thanks for the links.<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (L) Well then that eliminates the next question, which was a follow up. What fluid flow is it?<br /><br />A: As yet unknown organic structure throughout the body carrying a different fluid other than blood or lymph that is related to light. Your ancestors glowed and transmitted light and power.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><b>Don Juan:</b><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">“The smoke will help you see people like threads of light.<br /><br />- Threads of light?<br /><br />- Yes, threads, like white cobwebs. Very thin fibers running from the head to the navel. A person becomes like an egg made of living threads. His legs and arms resemble luminous silk hairs, emitting light in all directions.&quot;</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17410,"user":"Arlind","date":"2024-04-03T00:47:17+0200","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T17:58:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2483,"user":"Charlie","date":"2024-01-25T03:30:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":8800,"user":"SMM","date":"2024-01-23T19:21:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11459,"user":"ToxicCoward","date":"2024-01-22T22:57:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6869,"user":"artofdream","date":"2024-01-21T05:38:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-20T19:49:11+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T01:05:10+0100","react