024-01-16T18:45:27+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":6460,"user":"Puma","id":1155708,"date":"2024-01-16T18:30:03+0100","text":"Thanks to Laura, Andromeda and Saint Pierre and everyone involved in bringing us this session.<br /><br /><b><span style=\"font-size: 22px\">Milei and his desire to legalize the &quot;market&quot; for human organs</span></b><br /><br />About the tunnels found in Brooklyn and their use<br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(Joe) Human trafficking, organ trafficking?<br /><br />A: Whatever you can think of but mainly children.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 11007\" data-quote=\"Bluegazer\" data-source=\"post: 1155596\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155596\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155596\">Bluegazer said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">That said by the C&#039;s I now understand some things. And one of those things is the case of the current president of Argentina, Javier Milei, and his association with the Lubavitch sect.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote> Indeed<br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\">What does the president of Argentina have to do with the illegal clandestine tunnel system discovered these days in the Hasidic Jewish sector in New York City?<br /><br />Well, this is the first place Milei visited after winning the presidential election. Known as the <b>Chabad-Lubavitch</b> community. When Milei was elected president of Argentina he had an <b>URGENCY</b> to visit the grave of Rebbe Menachem Mendl Schneerson, who in his lifetime asked Netanyahu to do something to <b>hasten the coming of the messiah. </b><br /><br /><div class=\"bbMediaWrapper\" data-media-site-id=\"youtube\" data-media-key=\"rHBiT6eJaQQ\"><div class=\"bbMediaWrapper-inner\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rHBiT6eJaQQ?wmode=opaque\"width=\"560\" height=\"315\"frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div><br />Immediately afterward, he would become Israel&#039;s youngest Prime Minister.<br /><br />Netanyahu had visited the Rabbi to get his blessing for his &quot;<b>personal and political&quot;</b> success. Yes, exactly as Milei did to win the presidency of Argentina.<br /><br />In Milei&#039;s case, he asked the <b>Rebbe&#039;s soul</b> to help him become president of Argentina:<br /><br />&quot;The truth is that I did not get to know the Rebbe personally, but just in the last year I had the privilege of visiting the Rebbe&#039;s tomb twice. There I asked for his holy blessing to be elected president of Argentina and this blessing came true this week&quot;, Milei told Kfar Chabad, a Chabad newspaper in Israel.<br /><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/milei-saluda-a-eduardo-elsztain-luego-de-un-rezo-giah7oturzgzxc4qyrz3gcpkay-jpg.89932/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73095-64182c81fd4dd26e2b6bde8c69dc36bb.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"milei-saluda-a-eduardo-elsztain-luego-de-un-rezo-GIAH7OTURZGZXC4QYRZ3GCPKAY.jpg\"title=\"milei-saluda-a-eduardo-elsztain-luego-de-un-rezo-GIAH7OTURZGZXC4QYRZ3GCPKAY.jpg\"width=\"150\" height=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a><br /><br />This reminds us of Jeffrey Epstein&#039;s island and how he worked for the Mossad to blackmail politicians and show business. One cannot help but wonder if Milei and Netanyahu used the influence of the Jewish community and the Mossad. That is, if networks were moved in order to <b>achieve political success for both of them...(</b>or what sorceries or child sacrifices to Moloch were used to achieve the &quot;blessings&quot;.)<br />&#8203;</div><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \"><div style=\"text-align: justify\">NYC Jewish Chabad tunnel-temple has been linked to child sexual abuse for at least 30 years.&#8203;</div></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><div style=\"text-align: justify\"><div class=\"bbOembed bbMediaJustifier\"  data-media-site-id=\"twitter\"  data-media-key=\"1744758270475014289\"  data-xf-init=\"oembed\"  data-provider=\"twitter\"  data-id=\"1744758270475014289\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/x/status/1744758270475014289\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa--xf fab fa-twitter fa-twitter-square\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>https://twitter.com/x/status/1744758270475014289</a></div><br />It was precisely beneath the Chabad Lubavitch world headquarters in Brooklyn that an extensive system of subway tunnels was found leading to what appears to be an abandoned <b>mikveh (ritual bath). </b><br /><br />Videos taken with camera phones show a wall that hid the entrance, along with a bed with what appeared to be a bloodstain. <br />&#8203;</div><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 11007\" data-quote=\"Bluegazer\" data-source=\"post: 1155596\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155596\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155596\">Bluegazer said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">The question here is that since I have been examining the how and why of Javier Milei&#039;s career and his rise to the presidency, it is now clear to me (and until now it was an assumption that I did not dare to comment on because of the seriousness of the matter) that Milei shares this same hatred for humanity.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\">I had not considered Milei&#039;s hatred for humanity either, but it is true and he disguises it with what he calls &quot;<b>paleo-libertarianism</b>&quot; which is something like Darwinism applied to economics, i.e., survival of the fittest.<br /><br />And if, for example, the strongest needs an organ to survive, he has the right, under the viewpoint of paleo-libertarianism, to buy it and the weakest to sell it.<br /><br />&quot;My first property is my body, why shouldn&#039;t I be able to dispose of my body?&quot;...&quot;There are 7,500 people suffering, waiting for transplants, something is not working well&quot;. &quot;What I propose is to look for <b>market mechanisms </b>to solve this problem&quot; Milei said. <br /><br />He talks about the suffering of 7500 people to give an ethical and moral sense to his proposal, but be careful, he is talking about the <b>SALE</b> of organs, not about <b>DONATION</b>. Donation in his distorted vision is equal to communism, to subsidy, to aid, to distribution of wealth.<br /><br />&quot;There is no worse solution than the grip of the state. <b>The best thing is individuals acting freely.</b> Every time there is an intervention, the subsequent result is worse than what you had,&quot; Milei said. <br /><br />The problem is also that we have already seen the result of <b>mentally ill people acting freely.</b><br /><br /><div class=\"bbOembed bbMediaJustifier\"  data-media-site-id=\"twitter\"  data-media-key=\"1745155178192404924\"  data-xf-init=\"oembed\"  data-provider=\"twitter\"  data-id=\"1745155178192404924\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/x/status/1745155178192404924\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa--xf fab fa-twitter fa-twitter-square\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>https://twitter.com/x/status/1745155178192404924</a></div></div>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17410,"user":"Arlind","date":"2024-04-03T01:10:03+0200","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T18:04:22+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9854,"user":"oli 518","date":"2024-01-24T00:41:12+0100","reaction":"Angry"},{"user_id":8800,"user":"SMM","date":"2024-01-23T19:23:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11459,"user":"ToxicCoward","date":"2024-01-22T23:00:33+0100","reaction":"Angry"},{"user_id":5556,"user":"freigeist2.0","date":"2024-01-21T20:04:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17361,"user":"seve","date":"2024-01-21T15:24:54+0100","reaction":"Angry"},{"user_id":6869,"user":"artofdream","date":"2024-01-21T05:46:39+0100","reaction":"Sad"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-21T05:19:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-20T19:59:52+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-01-20T16:14:11+0100","reaction":"Sad"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-20T09:15:19+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T01:40:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:43:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15344,"user":"Cassis","date":"2024-01-19T19:18