eBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (L) And so what we&#039;re doing is... and have your Ivermectin on hand, and...</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Mike Adams from Natural News has been talking about this for the past year or so. He has many &quot;insider contacts&quot;. So this is just confirmation that he was onto something.<br /><br />The common cold is very contagious but not lethal, while Ebola is the reverse. They are trying to get the very contagious factor mixed in with high lethality factor + hemorrhage for the scare factor. If it goes the way they wish, it&#039;s going to be an ugly one and people are going to go berserk...<br /><br />Regarding Ivermectin, I&#039;m not aware that it&#039;s available for purchase here in Canada. Does anyone have a lead where we can obtain it?<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(Joe) It sounds like a theme park you never wanna go to. [laughter]<br /><br />A: Create your own with prayer, awareness, diet, fasting, etc.<br /><br />Q: (L) So we create our own theme park and hold it in our mental space. Is that it?<br /><br />A: Yes.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Is there a thread dedicated to such topics or techniques? I&#039;m not very familiar with meditation or prayers. I consider myself in kindergarten on that topic  <img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"😅\" title=\"Grinning face with sweat    :sweat_smile:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f605.png\" data-shortname=\":sweat_smile:\" />","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17410,"user":"Arlind","date":"2024-04-03T04:02:04+0200","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17406,"user":"Pat","date":"2024-01-26T23:50:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T18:10:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6869,"user":"artofdream","date":"2024-01-21T08:49:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-01-20T21:07:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-20T20:08:24+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-20T10:37:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T02:30:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:47:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-19T22:19:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15344,"user":"Cassis","date":"2024-01-19T19:24:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-19T18:09:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3693,"user":"JEEP","date":"2024-01-19T06:03:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10028,"user":"Cassandra94","date":"2024-01-18T21:20:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-18T20:05:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7615,"user":"mimimari","date":"2024-01-18T17:17:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1601,"user":"rylek","date":"2024-01-18T14:58:02+0100","react