user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-16T21:53:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-16T21:05:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-01-16T20:56:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12829,"user":"ryu","date":"2024-01-16T20:54:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-16T20:53:17+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":15488,"user":"N1mTzo","id":1155757,"date":"2024-01-16T20:50:00+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 12697\" data-quote=\"youlik\" data-source=\"post: 1155669\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155669\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155669\">youlik said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">There was one website that had a lot of material translated into Russian. Almost everything until 2018. It seems that they stopped working that year, but the site was available, you could read it, and for some time now, for some unknown reason, this site is unavailable.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 9769\" data-quote=\"Altair\" data-source=\"post: 1155679\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155679\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155679\">Altair said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">You probably mean the <a href=\"http://dreamland-exit.info\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Dreamland</a> website. They had unofficial Google translations of bad quality, and we have nothing to do with them. Besides, their website is closed since several years.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>dreamland had a catalog (navigation) of sessions by year and month in a convenient format - a couple of mouse clicks (the desired year, month) and you can read the transcript. The site is still accessible through web.archive.org (but it has not been updated for a long time, since approximately 2018). Probably they did not pay for hosting (this has already happened in past years) or the person who paid for the site has passed away, I don’t know.<br />In the current forum design, reading transcripts of sessions is not very convenient. More precisely, it is inconvenient to look for something from sessions that took place years ago (after all, you cannot save everything in your memory). Especially if you have problems with English (like me).<br />We need a catalog of transcripts of sessions in Russian by year/month in a simple text format (txt, html) and with clear navigation, like the dreamland website was. This would greatly help with the research that each of us is (hopefully) doing and sharing with others.<br />This is a wish, of course. Such work would take time (it doesn’t exist!<img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"🙂\" title=\"Slightly smiling face    :slight_smile:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f642.png\" data-shortname=\":slight_smile:\" />).<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 9769\" data-quote=\"Altair\" data-source=\"post: 1155679\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155679\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155679\">Altair said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Actually, we have already <b>tons of material</b> translated into Russian:</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>We read in Russian and are grateful to you for these translations!","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T18:16:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-21T09:56:04+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-01-20T21:13:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-20T20:25:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T03:12:02+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:48:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-19T22:47:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-19T21:51:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7615,"user":"mimimari","date":"2024-01-18T17:22:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-18T10:43:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":882,"user":"latulipenoire","date":"2024-01-18T01:19:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17335,"user":"forest_light","date":"2024-01-18T00:17:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-17T23:54:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5,"user":"herondancer","date":"2024-01-17T20:18:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-17T19:56:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-17T19:33:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-17T17:41:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4845,"user":"naorma","date":"202