n":"Like"},{"user_id":14284,"user":"iamthatis","date":"2024-01-17T00:16:29+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":4706,"user":"stellar","id":1155806,"date":"2024-01-16T23:38:51+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 12697\" data-quote=\"youlik\" data-source=\"post: 1155650\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155650\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155650\">youlik said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">It&#039;s just a huge session, so many interesting things! Thanks to all the participants!.<br />As a Russian and as a resident of Russia, of course, I am particularly interested in everything that concerns Russia and the Slavs in general.<br /><br />In this case, a very interesting question and answer, definitely meaningful, but this meaning escapes me. This answer can be interpreted in many ways. Who has any interpretations? Share it.<br /><br /><div class=\"bbCodeSpoiler\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-button button--longText button\" data-xf-click=\"toggle\" data-xf-init=\"tooltip\" title=\"Click to reveal or hide spoiler\"><span class=\"button-text\"><span>Spoiler: <span class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-button-title\">Russian spelling</span></span></span></button><div class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--spoiler\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\">Просто огромная сессия, столько всего интересного! Спасибо всем участникам!.<br /> Мне, как русскому и как жителю России конечно же особо интересно все, что касается России, славянства в целом.<br /> В данном случае очень интересный вопрос и ответ, однозначно осмысленный, но смысл этот от меня ускользает.  Этот ответ можно трактовать многими способами. У кого есть какие интерпретации? Поделитесь.</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>I would say, translate more into Russian language to make the information more accessible. FWIW","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T18:21:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-21T19:50:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-21T16:34:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-01-20T21:25:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-20T20:31:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3936,"user":"Andrian","date":"2024-01-20T19:41:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T04:03:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:53:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7615,"user":"mimimari","date":"2024-01-19T16:06:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-18T12:04:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-18T11:00:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":882,"user":"latulipenoire","date":"2024-01-18T02:33:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-17T19:19:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-17T17:50:11+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-17T14:54:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12829,"user":"ryu","date":"2024-01-17T13:19:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-17T10:46:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-01-17T09:41:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3990,"user":"Damian","date":"2024-01-17T01:31:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6538,"user":"tschai","date":"2024-01-17T00:52:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14181,"user":"Wandering Star","date":"2024-01-17T00:39:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-17T00:27:56+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":19544,"user":"meadow_wind","id":1155807,"date":"2024-01-16T23:41:49+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 18714\" data-quote=\"Freya Stewart\" data-source=\"post: 1155750\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155750\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155750\">Freya Stewart said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Hi <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/members/19544/\" class=\"username\" data-xf-init=\"member-tooltip\" data-user-id=\"19544\" data-username=\"@meadow_wind\">@meadow_wind</a>,<br />The Session from May 18, 2019 discusses things we can do to protect ourselves.<br /><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--unfurl    js-unfurl fauxBlockLink\"data-unfurl=\"true\" data-result-id=\"8123\" data-url=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/session-18-may-2019.47219/\" data-host=\"cassiopaea.org\" data-pending=\"false\"><div class=\"contentRow\"><div class=\"contentRow-figure contentRow-figure--fixedSmall js-unfurl-figure\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/img/FB_sky.jpg\" alt=\"cassiopaea.org\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\"/></div><div class=\"contentRow-main\"><h3 class=\"contentRow-header js-unfurl-title\"><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/session-18-may-2019.47219/\"class=\"link link--internal fauxBlockLink-blockLink\"target=\"\"rel=\"\"data-proxy-href=\"\">Session 18 May 2019</a></h3><div class=\"contentRow-snippet js-unfurl-desc\">Session Date: May 18th 2019  Laura, Andromeda, and Artemis at the board  Pierre, Joe, Chu, Ark, PoB, Scottie, Niall, Pikabu zee Cat, Noko the Wonderdog, Princess Leia, The Lunar Module  Q: (L) It is May the 18th, 2019. [Review of those present]  A: Good evening children! Joyeaeia of Cassiopaea...</div><div class=\"contentRow-minor contentRow-minor--hideLinks\"><span class=\"js-unfurl-favicon\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/styles/cass/img/favicon.png\" alt=\"cassiopaea.org\" class=\"bbCodeBlockUnfurl-icon\"data-onerror=\"hide-parent\"/></span>cassiopaea.org</div></div></div></div><br />This section here:<br /><br /><br />Here is a link to Eiruiu Eolas, the meditation program that Laura developed: <a href=\"https://eiriu-eolas.org/online-version/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Online Version – Éiriú Eolas</a><br /><br />The prayer of the soul is practiced at the end of the program. I enjoy using this one daily usually in the evening. There are also weekly online group sessions available: <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/eiriu-eolas-online-workshops-and-practice-public.48570/page-109#post-1155414\" class=\"link link--internal\">Éiriú-Eolas Online Workshops and Practice - Public</a><br /><br />There is also the Cassiopaean Crystal Project: <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/crystal-requests.49602/\" class=\"link link--internal\">Crystal Requests!</a><br />There are some prayers included with the crystals that are said daily. I&#039;m sorry, but I don&#039;t have a digital copy of these and am not sure where they are located on the site.<br /><br />In the last session posted, <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/session-30-december-2023.54112/\" class=\"link link--internal\">Session 30 December 2023</a> ,<br />this was mentioned:<br /><br /><br />I was thinking when this came out, that it might be a nice addition to read aloud along with daily prayers. Hope this helps!</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Thank you for trying to help, but I was already aware of all those things. I even created documents to print for easy access to members:<br /><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--unfurl    js-unfurl fauxBlockLink\"data-unfurl=\"true\" data-result-id=\"191295\" data-url=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/files-to-print-for-easy-access.54138/\" data-host=\"cassiopaea.org\" data-pending=\"false\"><div class=\"contentRow\"><div class=\"contentRow-figure contentRow-figure--fixedSmall js-unfurl-figure\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/img/FB_sky.jpg\" alt=\"cassiopaea.org\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\"/></div><div class=\"contentRow-main\"><h3 class=\"contentRow-header js-unfurl-title\"><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/files-to-print-for-easy-access.54138/\"class=\"link link--internal fauxBlockLink-blockLink\"target=\"\"rel=\"\"data-proxy-href=\"\">Files to print for easy access</a></h3><div class=\"contentRow-snippet js-unfurl-desc\">I&#039;m not sure where to post this nor which title to give (Moderators: feel free to modify).  I&#039;m making a notebook with the most important things as reminders. I made Word/PDF documents for printing.  It might interest other members to have them also. Right now I made 2 files. I will add more...</div><div class=\"contentRow-minor contentRow-minor--hideLinks\"><span class=\"js-unfurl-favicon\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/styles/cass/img/favicon.png\" alt=\"cassiopaea.org\" class=\"bbCodeBlockUnfurl-icon\"data-onerror=\"hide-parent\"/></span>cassiopaea.org</div></div></div></div><br />My question was specifically about: &quot;create our own theme park and hold it in our mental space&quot;, which is related to prayer and meditation techniques.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-25T18:21:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-21T19:50:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-01-20T21:26:22+0100","react