ek said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Thank you for another session.<br />So much information to analyze to learn.<br />Perfect timing as usual.<br />Great questions.<br />I was horrified by those tunnels used for child trafficking.<br />I wonder if the same thing is happening under other Chabad Lubavitch sect headquarters in other countries too?<br />Maybe Polish MP Grzegorz Braun, the one who extinguished the menorah with a fire extinguisher and later made a statement that he did it because Chabad Lubavitch is a satanic sect and will not allow such a presence in parliament, maybe he knows what they do underground?</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>I had similar thoughts. Maybe he is a man with a consciousness after all? Because in my logic I don&#039;t see any benefit of focusing attention on chabad-lubavitch for them or those involved. It only created more links for people, especially after finding the tunnels. Seeing how they are treated with honors in polish parliament and how politicians fear them (or more those hiding in their shadow...) I&#039;d say NY is not the only place where trafficking is ongoing.<br /><br />Or maybe it was all done on purpose? Braun&#039;s incident and the fact that the finding of tunnels was well documented and went public? But what the purpose might be?<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 153\" data-quote=\"ark\" data-source=\"post: 1155728\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155728\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155728\">ark said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Rare eyewitnesses say that there is a flattened arch protruding from the ground, under which there are many metal rooms, where even in the most severe frosts it is warm as in summer.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Metal rooms... I was immediately reminded of ancient metal rooms from Horizon Zero Dawn game. They were remnants of a previous fallen civilization destroyed by human-made combat robots. Of course people thought that it&#039;s linked to some religious rituals while in fact their purpose was simply practical. <br /><br /><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/1705479009817-png.89967/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73130-4a9b5b036f734f99fd0d6305c9b5fd14.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"1705479009817.png\"title=\"1705479009817.png\"width=\"188\" height=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-27T04:08:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13389,"user":"JACU CORBOTRONIK","date":"2024-01-25T11:03:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-21T20:45:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-21T16:48:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-20T04:59:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:55:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3693,"user":"JEEP","date":"2024-01-19T20:38:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-18T13:06:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-18T11:17:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-18T04:07:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5415,"user":"Skyalmian","date":"2024-01-18T02:54:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":882,"user":"latulipenoire","date":"2024-01-