nk link--external\" rel=\"noopener\">How to Get Rid of Stinky Mold in Your Washing Machine</a><br />Another<a href=\"https://www.today.com/news/your-washing-machine-growing-hidden-mold-6c10671363\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"noopener\"> site </a>suggests leaving the door open when the machine isn&#039;t in use to allow air flow, although they say to be careful if you have small children.<br /><br />P.S, thank you all for the session, it was jam packed and very thought provoking.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-27T04:12:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-21T22:44:27+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11608,"user":"nidO","date":"2024-01-21T20:23:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-21T16:52:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-01-21T06:19:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-21T02:28:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-21T00:06:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-20T23:49:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-20T20:42:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3936,"user":"Andrian","date":"2024-01-20T19:49:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7776,"user":"Carl","date":"2024-01-20T11:00:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10816,"user":"SummerLite","date":"2024-01-19T23:57:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-19T23:55:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5809,"user":"Breo","date":"2024-01-18T21:07:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-18T13:09:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-18T11:39:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9677,"user":"lainey","date":"2024-01-18T10:02:03+0100"