ought!<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (Ursus Minor) As the World Economic Forum starts promoting &#039;Disease X&#039; – what could it be?<br /><br />A: A big mistake that very well might take them out!<br /><br />Q: (Andromeda) So where&#039;s this Disease X gonna come from?<br /><br />A: Lab.<br /><br />Q: (Joe) And where is it likely to be released? Globally, or in one particular area?<br /><br />A: California, New York, Singapore, Paris, London.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>So, I&#039;m assuming awareness of the covid scheme is to wide spread world wide and this next attempt will be seen for what it is resulting in serious backlash. They will repeat the same patterns as before since their capacity for innovation is nonexistent. NYC was a main focus during Covid and it looks to be the same coming up. Considering the massive problems they&#039;re having with migrants perhaps this offers a solution. Spread the disease and take out more citizens who have likely had many jabs, which will free up living accommodations for the illegals who haven&#039;t been jabbed. Housing crisis solved.<br /><br />I had thought, the next outbreak would be caused by 5G frequency changes but according to this its an actual pathogen. Maybe 5G is another plan.<br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWat