y Kim","date":"2024-01-17T19:51:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14284,"user":"iamthatis","date":"2024-01-17T19:48:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-17T19:46:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-01-17T19:44:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-17T19:27:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-17T19:18:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-17T19:16:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-17T19:02:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-17T18:51:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10829,"user":"Jtucker","date":"2024-01-17T18:44:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7776,"user":"Carl","date":"2024-01-17T18:05:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":27,"user":"Beau","date":"2024-01-17T17:33:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7948,"user":"irjO","date":"2024-01-17T17:29:25+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":4888,"user":"Alma.Innovadora","id":1156007,"date":"2024-01-17T17:46:16+0100","text":"Thanks fore the amazing session! <img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"🙏\" title=\"Folded hands    :pray:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f64f.png\" data-shortname=\":pray:\" /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(seek10) What is the purpose of face peeling in the Los Pela Caras incidents?<br /><br />A: Side effect of exposure to 4D STS energy similar to radiation.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />A good reason not to stay and watch anything, stay away! we have to run from the place! <br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(L) Oh, you were just curious. You did not even stop to consider whether this question was universally interesting. Okay, well, we&#039;ll ask anyway. What was it?<br /><br />A: Usual window faller. We warned about increasing frequency of such encounters.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />But why do they always look like shadows? <img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"🤔\" title=\"Thinking face    :thinking:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f914.png\" data-shortname=\":thinking:\" /> we never see anything definite, they just look like spots as if something around them prevents you from being able to see them completely. How is something so big seen by few?... and all these beings are &quot;hostile&quot;. They come from anywhere in the universe is to kill and eat!... Do we have such a good taste in all our existence? the intergalactic McDonalds or what? <img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"🤣\" title=\"Rolling on the floor laughing    :rofl:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f923.png\" data-shortname=\":rofl:\" /> <br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(L) You&#039;re just trying to be tricky, aren&#039;t you? [laughter] Okay. Are aliens going to be introduced this year?<br /><br />A: As far as we can see, they have already been introduced, just the people are not paying attention.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />Yup!... and I don&#039;t know how to say it exactly but &quot;something feels in the environment&quot;, I feel a kind of tension, that &quot;something is approaching&quot;, a restlessness. I do not know where this internal &quot;alert&quot; comes from. <b>There&#039;s some disturbance in the force!</b> (laughs).","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-28T07:04:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-22T22:35:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-22T00:39:40+0100","reaction":"Haha"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-21T23:05:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-21T20:23:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-21T17:01:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17361,"user":"seve","date":"2024-01-21T15:44:45+0100","reaction":"Haha"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-01-21T13:49:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios"