naan","date":"2024-01-17T19:28:06+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-17T19:19:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-17T19:17:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-17T19:03:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-17T18:52:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10829,"user":"Jtucker","date":"2024-01-17T18:44:02+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-17T18:05:44+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":8422,"user":"mariowil7","id":1156012,"date":"2024-01-17T18:02:54+0100","text":"Thanks Laura, The C&#039;s, The Chateau Crew et. al.<br />This is a very dense session... So many things to consider...<img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/smoking.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":cool2:\" title=\"Smoking    :cool2:\" data-shortname=\":cool2:\" /><img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/smoking.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":cool2:\" title=\"Smoking    :cool2:\" data-shortname=\":cool2:\" /><img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/smoking.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":cool2:\" title=\"Smoking    :cool2:\" data-shortname=\":cool2:\" /><img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/smoking.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":cool2:\" title=\"Smoking    :cool2:\" data-shortname=\":cool2:\" />","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-28T07:04:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-22T22:36:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-21T23:05:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-21T20:23:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-21T17:02:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-01-21T13:49:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"