bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote> Yes, as Laura said, a dead Presbyterian is just that, a dead Presbyterian. But lately The Cs told us that after the transfer from 3rd to 4th density happen, you won&#039;t automatically be aware of it. That for a number of people, possibly lacking the knowledge and awareness they will still be a transfer. <br /> Question is, can a soul in 3rd density lacking the knowledge of level of density be transferred to a 4th. Is the knowledge a precondition or can awareness be acquired once transferred. I&#039;m thinking that it can and that it is not necessary but I&#039;m not sure.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-04-01T21:11:25+0200","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-02T16:16:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-28T07:11:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-23T19:13:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-22T16:43:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-22T00:50:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3936,"user":"Andrian","date":"2024-01-20T19:58:27+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-20T00:01:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-19T16:41:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7850,"user":"Ðekel","date":"2024-01-19T16:12:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7840,"user":"Stoneboss","date":"2024-01-19T04:28:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-01-19T04:21:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-18T18:48:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10630,"user":"JeanneT","date":"2024-01-18T14:12:11+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"202