e Cs&#039;, the Chateau crew, this Forum, the Red Pill books and Sott.net, without forget all the editors and translators in different languages, and all those involved in passing on all this knowledge from which we can learn on so many subjects. <img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/hug.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":hug2:\" title=\"Hug    :hug2:\" data-shortname=\":hug2:\" /><br /><br />Today it&#039;s even more important -it seems that as the months go by, this is the case, a little more each time, <b>but we were made for these times, don&#039;t forget</b>- to sort things out, decipher what is true from what is false, pay close attention to what is happening around us, to keep a cool head, to look to the right and to the left, taking care of those we love, and to have faith in the Cosmic Mind, who knows what it&#039;s doing.<br /><br />Darkness only exists to bring out the light, and as Pierre said during the last session: &quot;Glory for all&quot;, so we have something to hold on to while the darkness seems to be closing in!","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17410,"user":"Arlind","date":"2024-04-03T05:31:55+0200","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":1739,"user":"anartist","date":"2024-02-10T03:39:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9854,"user":"oli 518","date":"2024-02-07T16:41:13+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":4487,"user":"iyan","date":"2024-02-06T10:04:24+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-03T17:37:57+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-29T02:41:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11608,"user":"nidO","date":"2024-01-27T05:19:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-25T19:16:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2292,"user":"Aeneas","date":"2024-01-25T11:32:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3693,"user":"JEEP","date":"2024-01-25T01:31:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19399,"user":"Faca Fritz","date":"2024-01-