vernment science&#039;...</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Did he? I must have missed that one. It could have been a one-time thing because he knows how corrupt &quot;gov science is&quot; (or anything gov. related) and always points it out in many ways. The guy is a CEO running multiple businesses, but I found that he seems to be genuinely caring about people&#039;s health. welfare and survival.<br /><br />I started skimming through that site in daily starting in December 2019. By March 2020, I was one of the rare ones who knew the truth (from an interview with Prof. Francis Boyle who had found the paper trail: it was a bioweapons that had been worked at North Carolina Univ. and had been transferred to Wuhan Lab.)<br />From there, I skimmed the site daily for 3 years for relevant data, and I don&#039;t remember having seen him trust those injections. It&#039;s actually from there that I found out how dangerous they were. <br /><br />I don&#039;t want to seem to preach for him because he is just human and surely imperfect, but I trust there is relevant info being posted on his site, thus we shouldn&#039;t, what&#039;s the expression? Throw the baby with the water? This expression always makes me laugh.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":1739,"user":"anartist","date":"2024-02-10T03:41:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-03T17:41:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-20T00:08:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-19T18:38:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17269,"user":"Lyndi Lama","date":"2024-01-19T17:32:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-19T05:50:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":679,"user":"Mark7","date":"2024-01-19T00:24:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-01-18T22:33:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-18T17:02:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-18T16:17:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4518,"user":"Adobe","date":"2024-01-18T15:19:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-01-18T14:46:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14181,"user":"Wandering Star","date":"2024-01-18T14:36:02+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-18T14:26:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-18T14:14:52+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":8877,"user":"Persej","id":1156281,"date":"2024-01-18T14:28:28+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 274\" data-quote=\"Niall\" data-source=\"post: 1156252\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1156252\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1156252\">Niall said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Beware: it could equally be confirmation that he&#039;s being used by insiders to lay down misinformation in the alternative media scene. I&#039;ll never forget that Mike Adams, whose entire shtick had always been &#039;the coming NWO via bioweapons&#039;, told people in 2020 to &#039;trust the government science&#039;...</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Yes, Mike Adams <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/coronavirus-pandemic-apocalypse-now-or-exaggerated-scare-story.48214/post-861698\" class=\"link link--internal\">actively promoted</a> the Covid hysteria.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024