to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />(L) Yeah, or more like...<br /><br />A: Difficult to explain since you don&#039;t have the concepts.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Is it the warm invisible fluid suddenly touching the top of your head and flowing down on your neck and spine that you feel when getting Reiki or &quot;growing out of your shoes&quot;? ==&gt; When you are getting a mind-expansion? I had above fluid sensation and became tele-empathic for about 60 seconds and could palpably feel &amp; visualize the &#039;thoughts + emotions&#039; of my angrily arguing colleagues in ~2003. So is it that fluid?<br /><br />Gurdjieff stood by the door - recounted in the book of <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Gurdjieff-Women-Rope-1935-1939-1948-1949/dp/0955909066\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Women of the Rope</a> - and her apprentice woman standing by the window at other end of room declared:<br />- Oh! You are touching me!<br />Gurdjieff standing by the door:<br />- No. I&#039;m not.<br />This was a specific exercise / demonstration Gurdjieff proposed.<br /><br />Is it that kind of fluid? A <span style=\"color: rgb(85, 57, 130)\">warm release flow all over the tissues</span> - through skin and muscle mass - in your legs or spine or torso / in your side a teacupful of warm released fluid-like flowing feeling <u>inside your body</u>?","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-03T17:53:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T00:07:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-22T21:45:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17361,"user":"seve","date":"2024-01-21T15:56:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-21T05:54:11+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635