=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Bone broth! :D    <a href=\"https://floravita.superwebaruhaz.hu/zselatin-sertes-floragel-100-bloom-250g-nagy-tisztasagu-etkezesi-hidrolizalt-kollagen-t147542\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">This is the collagen I now use: <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">notice the amino-acid list by scrolling down</span>.</a><br />I also always cook the hardened bacon skins (10th of an inch thickness) [after I strip off the white soft bacon from the top] together with the marrow bones. Put into the freezer such broth solidifies into yellow transparent jelly. Mixed into pig soup - heated up via boiling since I put farm butter into it as well and it is recommended you always boil butter - if I mix enough such yellow-jelly broth into my soup and eat it, <span style=\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176)\">it &#039;glues my lips together&#039;</span>. As Laura recommended, I think bones should be cooked so long so they can be <a href=\"https://www.bollerbolt.hu/img/50559/20098/20098.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">force-pressed into &quot;bone-sand</a>&quot;. And this sand should be eaten, I think carefully in small amounts to avoid constipation.<br /><br />Collagen, the not-finely ground type [the not-recommended probably harder to digest sort] coagulates into a chewable &quot;gum&quot;, which takes a long time to dissolve in your mouth.  Finely ground collagen (around &#039;100 bloom&#039;), properly dissolves in soup and when I mix in three or more heaped teaspoons, <span style=\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176)\">it &#039;glues my lips together&#039;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 57, 130)\">.</span><br /><br />Two different lines of nutrition I think we are talking about here. Probably this can be proven by a scientifically trained academic, when researched: so both types of nutrition - broth &amp; collagen - may be beneficial. The body can use both in different ways.<br /><br />I called collagen important as I think I found a missing element in my research &#039;to completely replace carbs-laden snacks <a href=\"https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/evolutionary-psychiatry/201606/your-brain-folate\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">loaded with folates</a>. I tried only broth for 4-5 months last year and my brain was frozen, I couldn&#039;t work. Lost almost half a year in my magnum opus pension project. Was completely unable to produce high-quality products.. without snacks :( :(  So collagen replaces about 50% of my snacks ATM, so I eat half of the carbs now and still able to produce high quality work that sells.<br /><br />Unfortunately ATM I cannot cook broth all the time to eat it 30 days a month. I eat solid food for at least half a month, that&#039;s why I discovered pig collagen powders, which look like dried, yellowish sand with red particles mixed in, looks like as if it would be a &quot;ground down pig-marrow bone&quot;.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-02-06T14:22:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T00:13:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-22T22:05:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-22T19:04:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-21T16:20:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-20T00:09:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-19T20:44:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":360,"user":"mabar","date":"2024-01-19T18:53:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10829,"user":"Jtucker","date":"2024-01-19T15:50:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-19T11:33:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-19T10:51:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4717,"user":"Jones","date":"2024-01-19T10:16:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12779,"user":"Lukasz","date":"2024-01-19T09:48:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4667,"user":"Tristan","date":"2024-01-18T22:16:40+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":4518,"user":"Adobe","date":"2024-01-18T21:50:58+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":8877,"user":"Persej","id":1156390,"date":"2024-01-18T21:58:41+0100","text":"Yes, that is the standard collagen that you can buy in health food stores. My father was drinking hydrolyzed collagen peptides.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-02-06T14:23:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T00:13:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-22T22:06:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-22T19:04:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-21T16:21:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-20T00:09:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-19T20:44:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-19T11:33:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-19T10:51:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12779,"user":"Lukasz","date":"2024-01-19T09:49:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":47,"user":"Ryan","date":"2024-01-19T05:16:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-19T00:50:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11382,"user":"Odin","date":"2024-01-19T00:07:43+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":9230,"user":"Global Warning","id":1156404,"date":"2024-01-18T22:55:06+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(L) 4D is really weird. I guess that would be like Grays or something, you know? Or something like the semi-plant-like beings that they grow in giant test tubes. Is that it?</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Is there anything more known about the semi-plant-like beings, or another being in the test tubes?<br /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">A: Part of underground 4D STS base [at the Skinwalker Ranch].</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">A: Part of the underground 4D STS base [at the Skinwalker Ranch].</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>You have a direct address for the 4D STS underground base on Earth, and you didn&#039;t ask anything about it. What structure does it have, what is it used for, and by whom? Does the nearly-military base know about that? What was the Skinwalker exactly? What are the bubbles of light, visible at the ranch—some sort of energy leak?<br /><br />The dogs at the ranch got once melted by something; what was it? What scared the yogist?<br /><br />There were some things that probably became a mental projection of some 4D stuff, like dogs smoking cigarettes, reminding me of the hypnotic visions created with the abductions; the most funny I&#039;ve heard of were aliens frying cardboard pancakes, but also other stuff like teleported bulls. It&#039;s interesting, but I guess the answers would be generalized<br /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">&quot;Islam is the miscegenation of the worst of both Judaism and Christianity.&quot;</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>That&#039;s how I think of it<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (L) It&#039;s like we see reptilians as reptilians, but that may not necessarily be what they look like to themselves, right?<br /><br />(Andromeda) Because that&#039;s our interpretation of their essence.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>How do the Reptalians see themselves? How do they see humans?<br /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">A: Usual window faller. We warned about increasing frequency of such encounters.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>I wonder if they come back through the window or if we have to worry. Once it is seen, it is there. There was a bulletproof wolf on the Skinwalker ranch. So if they see such a gorilla, other people might be hurt?<br /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(L) What happened in Miami? I&#039;m curious to know too.<br /><br />A: CIA operation gone wrong necessitating coverup.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Thanks for solving it, was a bit bugging<br /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">circumcision...</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>I don&#039;t remember why did I quote it. Probably wasn&#039;t sure how is it stamping people so much. But I&#039;ve heard the same about sign of the cross at baptism. Despite the deeper level, probably something significantly affecting the psyche<br /><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Okay. Are aliens going to be introduced this year?<br /><br />A: As far as we can see, they have already been introduced, just the people are not paying attention.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(Andromeda) Press conferences, and all that.<br /><br />A: Not yet.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>It is telling directly that the aliens are going to be introduced, actually. But maybe indirectly. I just can&#039;t believe in it. So far, we&#039;ve had everything covered up. Lately, some information about UFOs has been declassified, and events have been randomly shown. And the Mexican cake aliens. Well, as you say, let&#039;s wait and see","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-02-06T14:26:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-29T02:52:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6284,"user":"Robert Fordisto","date":"2024-01-25T05:28:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-22T22:10:11+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17361,"user":"seve","date":"2024-01-21T15:59:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-19T20:46:25+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-19T11:34:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-19T10:52:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":882,"user":"latulipenoire","date":"2024-01-19T03:37:25+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","id":1156414,"date":"2024-01-18T23:56:02+0100","text":"Wow! Thank you. Really a lot to take in. This in particular really surprised me, <br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(Altair) What percentage of human souls in 5D are aware of the existence of 4th density?<br /><br />A: Small. One has to be aware of it before death. Otherwise it is veiled.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a