 it in the afternoon, thinking that among other good stuff I&#039;m getting my collagen in. <u>By boiling it every day, have I destroyed the collagen?  </u> If so, what kind of collagen would you recommend that I could buy to take in capsule form?</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />Yeah, it&#039;s recommended to make sure you don&#039;t boil your bone broth, as it denatures collagen. Making bone broth is a fine art! I also learned from an herbalist friend that another health food that denatures during heating is honey.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-02-06T14:26:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T07:39:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-26T03:29:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-23T19:55:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11120,"user":"Mr.Cyan","date":"2024-01-23T07:47:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-22T22:10:59+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-22T19:07:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-21T16:34:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-21T13:38:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-01-20T20:00:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-20T00:09:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-19T20:48:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-19T20:47:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-19T19:52:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12854,"user":"Tuulikki","date":"2024-01-19T13:50:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4518,"user":"