e one of the unlucky ones who easily trigger into intense fight/flight when leaving the dorsal vagal state so needs to have some gentle non-threatening mobilisation rather than being physically still. I think the statement is partially based on the fact that 80% of the fibres in the ANS are afferent or sensory and send signals back to the brain. 20% efferent fibres take signals from the brain to the various organs in the body. Even so, I think it is possible for the mind to learn to manage the autonomic nervous system as shown by the yogi practices.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>The following is an assumption, but when they talk about the subterraneans being dual-density and with variability in physicality, I have thought that they &quot;put their physical body to sleep&quot; and then use the multidimensional or fourth-density body.<br /><br />Something similar to what is called astral travel in various literature, but with a complete energy body, which allows interaction in the fourth density.<br /><br />There is control of the heart of the physical body at will.<br /><br />Just my guess on that.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-27T23:09:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T07:49:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-24T22:38:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-21T17:41:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12779,"user":"Lukasz","date":"2024-01-20T23:33:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-20T20:45:31+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11382,"user":"Odin","date":"2024-01-20T09:34:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-20T07:18:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-2