air said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">It actually makes sense. If 3D is a school, where most of the learning takes place, then in 5D the (in 3D acquired) knowledge can only be reflected upon but not expanded.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>My world makes sense again.  Thank you. This explains a lot actually and it has given me new hope and helped to quash some of my more nihilistic thoughts and tendencies.  What we see and do here has real meaning as some of this work just has to be done here.  I hope that makes sense.  Anyway, it&#039;s really got me thinking and thanks. <img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"🥰\" title=\"Smiling face with hearts    :smiling_face_with_3_hearts:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f970.png\" data-shortname=\":smiling_face_with_3_hearts:\" />","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":19399,"user":"Faca Fritz","date":"2024-02-12T10:30:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-29T03:02:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T07:58:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-26T03:52:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2292,"user":"Aeneas","date":"2024-01-25T13:03:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-24T22:46:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17310,"user":"Anya112003","date":"2024-01-23T20:22:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1789,"user":"axj","date":"2024-01-23T08:41:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-22T10:22:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-22T02:43:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-21T17:49:00+0100","reaction":"Like