s floating in the air between the ground/3D noise and outer space. <br /><br />It seems that this is a journey going from one place to another - back to 5D.<br /><br />We are here now and it’s important to know and learn but same time not be consumed and subsumed by the noise the 3D muck","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":11608,"user":"nidO","date":"2024-01-31T02:01:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-29T03:02:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T07:59:06+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-24T22:47:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-22T10:22:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-22T02:48:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-21T17:50:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-21T11:08:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12854,"user":"Tuulikki","date":"2024-01-21T05:54:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3936,"user":"Andrian","date":"2024-01-20T20:33:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7776,"user":"Carl","date":"2024-01-20T19:25:24+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11382,"user":"Odin","date":"2024-01-20T09:37:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-20T07:26:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-20T05:18:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4551,"user":"Emet-Selch","date":"2024-01-20T01:53:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-20T00:13:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-19T22:29:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-01-19T22:17:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-19T22:02:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Deb