or something between 20 or 50 dollars. Not bad at all! <br /><br />So yeah, if you&#039;re prepared, you shouldn&#039;t worry about the lethality of this virus. It reminds me what the Cs said in a prior session, that it&#039;s not really the lab created viruses that we have to worry about, but the 4D STS space ones.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":10461,"user":"iscreamsandwish","date":"2024-05-06T16:47:01+0200","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7512,"user":"Gwenllian","date":"2024-03-14T19:43:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15533,"user":"Deliverance","date":"2024-02-29T16:02:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19399,"user":"Faca Fritz","date":"2024-02-12T10:52:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18191,"user":"Uperios","date":"2024-02-08T21:34:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1957,"user":"Regulattor","date":"2024-02-07T16:36:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":8441,"user":"Nachtweide","date":"2024-02-02T06:29:00+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":11608,"user":"nidO","date":"2024-02-02T06:06:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-30T18:43:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12879,"user":"Harmony99","date":"2024-01-29T15:51:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1666,"user":"adam7117","date":"2024-01-28T12:43:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-27T23:20:31+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T08:01:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-26T17:54:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2292,"user":"Aeneas","date":"2024-01-25T13:08:57+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-24T22:53:36+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":11262,"user":"Matai","date":"2024-01-24T08:01:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1789,"user":"axj","date":"2024-01-23T18:38:31+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-01-23T18:05:30+0100","reaction":"Lik