s=\"member: 11868\" data-quote=\"Ursus Minor\" data-source=\"post: 1156927\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1156927\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1156927\">Ursus Minor said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">The ivermectin tablets (6 mg) I bought have a production date of 04/2021 and are said to expire 03/2024. My questions would be similar to <i>echo&#039;s.</i><br /><br />The hydroxychloroquine of early 2022 expired in 05/2023.<br /><br />On the subject of alibaba purchases I would like to ask our German members whether they have succeeded getting ivermectin through that channel since I personally couldn&#039;t get my deliveries from India past the customs office at Frankfurt airport at that time.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"💊\" title=\"Pill    :pill:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f48a.png\" data-shortname=\":pill:\" /> will be harder to import in most countries<br />you&#039;d want to get the powder and declare something like &quot;pathogen X 3000 killer&quot; anything other than the malevolent ivermectin","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-30T19:39:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T08:29:53+0100","reaction":"Haha"},{"user_id":17335,"user":"forest_light","date":"2024-01-25T10:07:52+0100","reaction":"Haha"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-24T23:33:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-23T23:24:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-23T17:19:36+0100","reaction":"Haha"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-01-22T22:17:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-22T18:54:56+0100","reaction":"Haha"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-22T10:42:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-22T06:31:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2942,"user":"Bobo08","date":"2024-01-22T00:22:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-21T16:58:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":8690,"user":"Corvus","date":"2024-01-21T16:26:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":8877,"user":"Persej","date":"2024-01-21T14:20:54+0100","reaction":"Haha"}]},{"user_id":6460,"user":"Puma","id":1157077,"date":"2024-01-21T14:50:11+0100","text":"<span style=\"font-size: 22px\"><b>The jellyfish entity phenomenon seen with new eyes</b></span><br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (Approaching Infinity) Jeremy Corbell and George Knapp recently released a video from Iraq taken on a base in late 2017 of a strange jellyfish UFO that was visible only on thermal camera. It resembles many other videos people have taken over the years. The video itself has been confirmed as legitimate by a soldier who was stationed at the base who said they referred to it as the spaghetti monster. What was this object?<br /><br />A: 4D energy being that feeds on <b>human suffering</b></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/jellyfish-ufo-be-like-spawn-more-overlords-v0-7sb3b6hjegbc1-jpeg.90288/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73451-508c2b2f25863dbb5bd124b396175737.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"jellyfish-ufo-be-like-spawn-more-overlords-v0-7sb3b6hjegbc1.jpeg\"title=\"jellyfish-ufo-be-like-spawn-more-overlords-v0-7sb3b6hjegbc1.jpeg\"width=\"155\" height=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a><br />The Iraq jellyfish and an artistic interpretation of the object.<br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\"><br />Now that the Cs have clarified the jellyfish UFO phenomenon as a 4D being or a probe, I have another perspective on the phenomena that happened in Mexico and that were identified at the time as the sighting of a <b>witch and ghosts.</b><br /><br />The following video I posted in the &quot;Just weird videos&quot; thread shows a group of stray dogs barking at an object that appears to be descending. The video says that the object appeared very close to the bank of the Coatepec river. We know that this kind of phenomena occupy bodies of water as portals. <br />&#8203;</div><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 6460\" data-quote=\"Puma\" data-source=\"post: 1015790\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1015790\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1015790\">Puma said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">A video that was recorded on February 23, 2022 and that was released by the Mexican ufologist and journalist Jaime Maussan, shows the moment in which two alleged entities &quot;descend&quot; from the sky in the presence of three dogs that bark at them in San Vicente Chicoloapan, State of Mexico.<br /><br />The video lasting just over two minutes, was recorded at one in the morning with 36 minutes by a security camera near the Coatepec River, and in it two strange formations can be seen, with a transparent appearance that slowly descend in what appears to be a dump while three stray dogs bark and run frightened by the event.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><div class=\"bbOembed bbMediaJustifier\"  data-media-site-id=\"twitter\"  data-media-key=\"1503827133021446146\"  data-xf-init=\"oembed\"  data-provider=\"twitter\"  data-id=\"1503827133021446146\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/x/status/1503827133021446146\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa--xf fab fa-twitter fa-twitter-square\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>https://twitter.com/x/status/1503827133021446146</a></div><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\">By the way, Coatepec is a Nahuatl word that means &quot;hill of snakes&quot; There is a great tradition in Mesoamerican cultures for the worship of snakes as gods and we know that these gods were possibly the hyperdimensional 4D sts.&#8203;</div><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (L) It&#039;s like we see reptilians as reptilians, but that may not necessarily be what they look like to themselves, right?<br /><br />(Andromeda) Because that&#039;s our interpretation of their essence.<br /><br />(Niall) Even if it&#039;s the first time we encounter or see them...</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\">Now, there have been several apparitions of witches in the state of Nuevo Leon, in northern Mexico.<br /><br />In 2004, Leonardo Samaniego, a police officer in the State of Nuevo Leon, reported being attacked by a witch at 3:00 a.m. <br /><br />While patrolling in one of the neighborhoods adjacent to Cerro de la silla (a hill shaped like a saddle) and near a cemetery, suddenly, something large and black fell from one of the trees, but, to his surprise, the mysterious object did not touch the ground, but fluttered slowly, revealing its monstrous witch shape in front of the car&#039;s headlights. The police officer said the witch had feathers and claws with which she scratched the windshield.&#8203;</div><blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">(L) Since we are &quot;wave reading consciousness units&quot;, we read waves. So that&#039;s what people are doing when they see jellyfish, <b>they&#039;re reading the information...</b></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\">The supposed witch attacked the windshield as if trying to catch the policeman, but he reversed and crashed at the end of the street, but not before calling for help on the radio. His companions found the car wrecked and Leonardo passed out, possibly more from fear than from the blow.<br /><br />Shortly thereafter, Leonardo was interviewed by ufologist Jaime Maussan who showed him an artistic representation of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flatwoods_monster\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Flatwoods Monster </a>and the policeman said that the image was very similar to what he saw.<br /><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/flatwoods_monster-png.90295/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73458-b57f26cbd999040109f09501f488eb0f.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"Flatwoods_monster.png\"title=\"Flatwoods_monster.png\"width=\"100\" height=\"146\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a>&#8203;</div><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/images-jpeg.90296/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73459-416741f009f8af2044ebb984a9235e03.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"images.jpeg\"title=\"images.jpeg\"width=\"100\" height=\"145\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a><br /><br />Representation of what Leonardo Samaniego saw today known as the Witch of Guadalupe Nuevo Leon.<br /><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/20240121_073205-jpg.90298/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73461-4c1a012cb84d1f5d9c8ab601f1682890.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"20240121_073205.jpg\"title=\"20240121_073205.jpg\"width=\"176\" height=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a><br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify\">Another case that caused a stir was the alleged witch that was sighted on May 17, 2006 by members of the UFO group Club Nuevo Leon. The group filmed the flight of a humanoid figure that they say changed color, from red to black, because of the shape of the head or top, they concluded that it was a hood or beaked hat as witches are commonly depicted.&#8203;</div><br />The witnesses were at the top of the Cerro de las Mitras, (another hill) located in the town of Monterrey (State of Nuevo Leon).<br /><br /><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/attachments/ejmzbelxkaaxoyq-jpg.90297/\"target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/data/attachments/73/73460-5e29376a5073906c5fb9b904c922f793.jpg\"class=\"bbImage \"style=\"\"alt=\"EjMzbelXkAAXOYq.jpg\"title=\"EjMzbelXkAAXOYq.jpg\"width=\"171\" height=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a><br /><div class=\"bbMediaWrapper\" data-media-site-id=\"youtube\" data-media-key=\"A-vo8PkMh1Y\"><div class=\"bbMediaWrapper-inner\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/A-vo8PkMh1Y?wmode=opaque\"width=\"560\" height=\"315\"frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div><br />Were the witches and ghosts seen in Mexico a phenomenon similar to the Iraqi jellyfish UFO?","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":47,"user":"Ryan","date":"2024-03-24T06:05:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11608,"user":"nidO","date":"2024-02-06T06:32:20+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-30T19:41:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T08:31:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-27T06:36:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2292,"user":"Aeneas","date":"2024-01-26T17:31:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19607,"user":"Ajourneythroughthevoid","date":"2024-01-26T06:02:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17335,"user":"forest_light","date":"2024-01-25T10:12:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12854,"user":"Tuulikki","date":"2024-01-25T09:38:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-24T23:38:28+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":11120,"user":"Mr.Cyan","date":"2024-01-24T02:51:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-23T23:25:33+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-01-23T18:44:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-23T17:26:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_i