 lymph that is related to light. Your ancestors glowed and transmitted light and power.<br /><br />Q: (Joe) Was that related to the veins? They were talking about blue veins or the light coming from them... Wasn&#039;t there some session about it?</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />This was a thing with the Taelons in <a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0123816/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Earth Final Conflict</a> relating to exertion and/or psychic communication.  See <a href=\"https://earthfinalconflict.fandom.com/wiki/Blush\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Blush</a>.<br /><br />Interesting the range of sources &amp; traditions that the writers of that show drew from.  The aliens also moved their hands into <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mudra\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">mudra</a> when they talked.   Hmm, I see that last time I made a connection to that show was <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/session-14-january-2023.52926/post-1079622\" class=\"link link--internal\">this week a year ago</a>, how funny.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:38:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:32:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-25T08:07:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:03:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-23T20:52:25+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-01-22T20:00:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-22T19:21:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-22T19:15:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-22T16:59:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-22T16:44:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-22T14:13:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17269,"user":"Lyndi Lama","date":"2024-01-22T14:03:06+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","id":1157330,"date":"2024-01-22T14:17:46+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 13630\" data-quote=\"Stella Marys\" data-source=\"post: 1157315\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1157315\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1157315\">Stella Marys said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">I remember this part of a session. Session Date: February 27th 2016<br /><br /><br />This is something that has been happening for years with my husband (Bernardo GA), and we found it very curious. Even with our eyes closed. Sometimes they are a kind of &quot;flashes&quot;; others are these &quot;bursts&quot;. The strongest one was when I read a book that talked about Julius Caesar without knowing who he really was. In the dark, when we were in opposite positions on the bed, each on his side, we experienced a great flash of light in the darkness as if it were a fireball explosion. We both saw it in unison. This was the strangest thing we had ever experienced. In time we learned the truth about Julius Caesar. Now I have to leave and I don&#039;t have time to investigate what this &quot;phosphenes in the brain&quot; thing is. I will look for material later.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>It looks like it is a kind of stimulus (mechanic, electric or magnetic) that happens. So the variant electric and magnetic could be triggert by learning or realisation of something (change of FRV causes change of your electric/magnetic fields).<br /><br /><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phosphene\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Phosphene - Wikipedia</a>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:38:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-29T22:20:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:32:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4180,"user":"Lilou","date":"2024-01-28T04:21:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:12:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-27T06:55:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-25T08:10:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:03:57+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-01-24T06:12:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-23T19:49:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-23T17:45:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-01-23T11:53:25+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-23T09:47:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-01-22T20:01:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-22T19:43:20+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-22T19:21:27+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-22T19:16:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6460,"user":"Puma","date":"2024-01-22T19:15:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":86,"user":"Ca.","date":"2024-01-22T18:18:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5384,"user":"Maya","date":"2024-01-22T17:59:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-22T17:44:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-22T16:59:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-22T16:45:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14181,"user":"Wandering Star","date":"2024-01-22T15:34:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19468,"user":"ImaPrototype","date":"2024-01-22T14:34:10+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","id":1157386,"date":"2024-01-22T17:39:47+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 9769\" data-quote=\"Altair\" data-source=\"post: 1155715\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155715\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155715\">Altair said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">It actually makes sense. If 3D is a school, where most of the learning takes place, then in 5D the (in 3D acquired) knowledge can only be reflected upon but not expanded.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Hi Altair. Are you saying that gaining knowledge and learning is just reduced to reflecting and contemplation in 5D? I cannot see where the progress is in that. Unless we already know everything already - which I doubt, unless we have already recycled from 1st to 6th already and have reached 3D again. <br />If knowledge is something you wish to continue to pursue, which I certainly DO, why would there not be the equivalent of guides or &#039;halls of learning&#039; etc. Why just contemplate your navel until you reincarnate?<br /><br />Obviously there is plenty of opportunities to charitably help, and be part of teams for such work, which is always required. Including reviewing your past live, which is also essential for progress. <br />There is also a choice as to how long you remain in 5D before reincarnating for some people. Not all recycle very quickly. I cannot see that creativity or learning is not expanded upon - or at least I have never heard of that before now.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":13215,"user":"ApotheosisMMC.","date":"2024-03-29T05:05:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:40:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:13:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-25T08:11:24+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1789,"user":"axj","date":"2024-01-23T22:03:20+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-23T20:52:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-23T17:46:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-23T06:17:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18714,"user":"Freya Stewart","date":"2024-01-23T01:03:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-23T00:39:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-01-22T20:02:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4518,"user":"Adobe","date":"2024-01-22T20:01:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13564,"user":"SlipNet","date":"2024-01-22T17:53:42+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":114,"user":"genero81","id":1157391,"date":"2024-01-22T17:54:59+0100","text":"I think it has to do with the belief center. We&#039;ve been given some big clues by the C&#039;s over the years. One of my favorites; &quot;Remember density refers to conscious awareness only, once one becomes aware, all conforms to that awareness.&quot; This is something that continues in 5D. I&#039;ve been consciously working to expand my awareness while here in 3D so hopefully, I can finish up any lessons still needed at 5D and incarnate next round in 4D. That&#039;s my hope anyway. The more you can become aware of now, the greater your access in 5D. OSIT","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":47,"user":"Ryan","date":"2024-03-24T06:27:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:40:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3726,"user":"3DStudent","date":"2024-01-30T19:06:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:34:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17307,"user":"Asa","date":"2024-01-28T22:59:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:13:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-27T06:56:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2292,"user":"Aeneas","date":"2024-01-26T18:57:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-01-25T08:11:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:05:09+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":385,"user":"Alana","date":"2024-01-24T09:36:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4601,"user":"987baz","date":"2024-01-24T01:46:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-23T20:53:52+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-23T19:49:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-23T18:22:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4163,"user":"Eboard10","date":"2024-01-23T18:10:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-23T17:47:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-23T13:33:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13103,"user":"Evan","date":"2024-01-23T12:14:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17361,"user":"seve","date":"2024-01-