Content \">I had my money on the jewish tunnels being used to ferry kids around,always nice to see one&#039;s observations confirmed even if the subject matter is grim.Thank you for the session.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Where the tunnels were under the buildings was by thecurrently disused Jewish womens centre. If it is similar to mosques then the women and children would be in the area that they were digging towards. Thus kidnapping their &#039;own&#039; children. And perhaps it was used by the females for other meetings during the week too. So that was what first struck me - the proximity of &#039;supply&#039;. Beyond evil.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:45:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:37:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:20:18+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-24T01:36:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11868,"user":"Ursus Minor","date":"2024-01-23T12:12:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-23T08:45:16+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-23T06:22:36+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-01-23T04:56:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18714,"user":"Freya Stewart","date":"2024-01-23T01:44:43+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-23T01:31:36+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-23T01:01:07+0100","reaction":"Wow"}]},{"user_id":4518,"user":"Adobe","id":1157433,"date":"2024-01-22T21:07:49+0100","text":"Hopefully this relates to the above conversation discussing: where is learning the best.<br /><br />Twice last week I woke up with the same interpretation or two different situation taking place in two different dream-a-spheres.<br /><br />Recently the C’s have said that while dreaming we could essentially be anywhere dimension or density, and I’ll add to that any “other place” too.<br /><br />In both scenarios the situation had become so nuanced that I said: I don’t understand anymore! It is too confusing! There are too many contributing factors. It can’t be done! Then I woke and for a VERY short period of time I remembered the situations and “here in 3D” I could understand it. Super nuanced for sure, <u>but not as bad as today’s news to understand.</u> I thought that maybe “here” actually is a better place to figure things out. And “there” it was easy to become overwhelmed.<br /><br />I can’t imagine 5D being a place where you can’t learn, but (just spit-balling here) maybe it’s similar to Don Juan’s recapitulation. <u>Recapitulation or contemplation zone.</u> You’ve already done it (in 3D) now in 5D you can sift through it from many angles and “see it” better. And, if after all that, “if you want” you can <u>build another scenario and go back</u> for another shot at it in 3D. Another though: maybe 5D is the book, and 3D is the practical application. Where you actually ride the bike.<br /><br />I’m sure most here came into this life <u>already just knowing some stuff</u>. Where did it come from? I’ve never question it accept to say its past lives, but maybe better said: Its 35353535353535353535353535353535… and sooner or later you get it.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":9854,"user":"oli 518","date":"2024-02-21T19:38:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:46:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-29T22:27:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:39:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19309,"user":"Alor","date":"2024-01-28T02:22:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:21:24+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-01-25T00:54:31+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:21:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5809,"user":"Breo","date":"2024-01-24T18:53:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-01-24T06:25:20+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4601,"user":"987baz","date":"2024-01-24T01:48:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-24T01:41:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-23T22:39:25+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-23T21:01:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-23T19:57:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12829,"user":"ryu","date":"2024-01-23T19:30:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4551,"user":"Emet-Selch","date":"2024-01-23T19:22:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-23T17:52:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10829,"user":"Jtucker","date":"2024-01-23T17:25:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-23T14:58:13+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13103,"user":"Evan","date":"2024-01-23T12:20:02+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-23T12:08:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17361,"user":"seve","date":"2024-01-23T10:39:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2268,"user":"Beorn","date":"2024-01-23T09:10:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-23T08:46:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-23T08:15:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-23T06:23:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-01-23T04:56:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":118,"user":"annp","date":"2024-01-23T03:34:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18714,"user":"Freya Stewart","date":"2024-01-23T01:45:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-23T01:35:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14181,"user":"Wandering Star","date":"2024-01-22T22:52:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12779,"user":"Lukasz","date":"2024-01-22T22:18:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2744,"user":"ramaj","date":"2024-01-22T22:08:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":76,"user":"Lucius","date":"2024-01-22T21:58:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-01-22T21:36:35+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":12697,"user":"youlik","id":1157436,"date":"2024-01-22T21:19:49+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 12487\" data-quote=\"Akul\" data-source=\"post: 1156999\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1156999\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1156999\">Akul said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Why are you going beyond a mere correction of some definition, writing a whole narrative defending a STS psychopathic system?</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Really, what am I trying to do?<br />In response, there are only propaganda cliches, fraud and outright lies, and all this in scientific language. &quot;I&#039;m not interested in playing dichotomous games&quot;- really? Scientific words do not add meaning.<br />And I also liked this one.: &quot;Look at your wording.&quot; I write in Russian and not always, obviously when translated it turns out like in Oxford or Cambridge, I&#039;m sorry. We have this kind of argument called: Eh! He also put on glasses.<br />In general, everything is &quot;so typical&quot;.<br />As there, in the Gospel of Matthew (ch. 7, v. 6): &quot;... do not throw your pearls before ...&quot;.<br /><br /><div class=\"bbCodeSpoiler\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-button button--longText button\" data-xf-click=\"toggle\" data-xf-init=\"tooltip\" title=\"Click to reveal or hide spoiler\"><span class=\"button-text\"><span>Spoiler: <span class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-button-title\">Russian spelling</span></span></span></button><div class=\"bbCodeSpoiler-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--spoiler\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\">Действительно, чегой то я стараюсь?<br /> В ответ одни пропагандистские штампы, подтасовки и прямая ложь и все это наукообразным языком. &quot;Мне не интересно играть в дихотомические игры&quot;- неужели? Наукообразные слова не добавляют смысла. <br />И еще вот это мне понравилось: &quot;Посмотрите на свою формулировку&quot;. Я пишу по русски и не всегда, очевидно при переводе получается как в оксфордах или кембриджах, уж извините. У нас такого рода аргументы называются: Э-эх! А еще он очки надел. <br />В общем все &quot;так типично&quot;.<br /> Как там, в Евангелии от Матфея (гл. 7, ст. 6) : «...не бросайте жемчуга вашего перед ...».</div></div></div></div>","attachments":[],"reactions":[]},{"user_id":19101,"user":"EmeraldR","id":1157446,"date":"2024-01-22T22:39:03+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 14284\" data-quote=\"iamthatis\" data-source=\"post: 1157192\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1157192\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1157192\">iamthatis said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">The water of life from fairy tales, or holy water used against vampires might not be some external substance, but something created in our bodies.<br /><br />Nov 22, 1997:<br /><br /><br /><br />Later on, there was this session that talks about the nature of water as etheric. It has me thinking of water as not just a thing, H20, a certain number of non-intelligent molecules, but as an entity, maybe sort of like a holy person or holy force who lives both inside us in our bodies and outside us in oceans, lakes, clouds and streams. This &#039;someone&#039; pervades our entire world and can help us so long as we pray and generate the proper intent.<br /><br /><br /><br />So we can talk to the water in a cup, and also talk to the water in our own body, and in so doing it&#039;s another way we can transform ourselves.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br /><br />Water is crucial !! excellent info - before reading this I purchased a reverse osmosis water device from sweden ! My qigong teacher really emphasised the importance of water on all levels and to try and drink hi quality water amongst other things !  Great confirmation from the C s on the importance of water !   thanks for posting<br /><br />anyone know about hydrogen water devices ?<br /><br /><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--unfurl    js-unfurl fauxBlockLink\"data-unfurl=\"true\" data-result-id=\"196519\" data-url=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/reverse-osmosis-water-filters.16479/\" data-host=\"cassiopaea.org\" data-pending=\"false\"><div class=\"contentRow\"><div class=\"contentRow-figure contentRow-figure--fixedSmall js-unfurl-figure\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/img/FB_sky.jpg\" alt=\"cassiopaea.org\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\"/></div><div class=\"contentRow-main\"><h3 class=\"contentRow-header js-unfurl-title\"><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/reverse-osmosis-water-filters.16479/\"class=\"link link--internal fauxBlockLink-blockLink\"target=\"\"rel=\"\"data-proxy-href=\"\">Reverse Osmosis Water Filters</a></h3><div class=\"contentRow-snippet js-unfurl-desc\">Hi all,  Have been weighing up investing in a Reverse Osmosis water filter for a while now.  Obviously there are many internet sites that sell them and the prices seem to vary greatly.  Does anyone who has one have any advice about what to look for?  I was thinking of fitting it myself as...</div><div class=\"contentRow-minor contentRow-minor--hideLinks\"><span class=\"js-unfurl-favicon\"><img src=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/styles/cass/img/favicon.png\" alt=\"cassiopaea.org\" class=\"bbCodeBlockUnfurl-icon\"data-onerror=\"hide-parent\"/></span>cassiopaea.org</div></div></div></div><img class=\"smilie smilie--emoji\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"👍\" title=\"Thumbs up    :thumbsup:\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/joypixels/assets/8.0/png/unicode/64/1f44d.png\" data-shortname=\":thumbsup:\" /><img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/thumbup.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":thup:\" title=\"Thumbs up    :thup:\" data-shortname=\":thup:\" />","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:47:22+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-29T22:28:22+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:41:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":118,"user":"annp","date":"2024-01-27T02:01:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:24:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-23T19:57:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12829,"user":"ryu","date":"2024-01-23T19:49:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15985,"user":"Blaza","date":"2024-01-23T19:12:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-23T17:53:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-23T14:59:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-23T12:09:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12779,"user":"Lukasz","date":"2024-01-23T10:02:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-23T08:46:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-23T08:16:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-01-23T06:49:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-01-23T06:42:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-23T06:26:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-01-23T04:56:53+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-01-23T04:43:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-23T01:43:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-23T01:02:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14284,"user":"iamthatis","date":"2024-01-22T23:08:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-01-22T22:40:09+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","id":1157456,"date":"2024-01-23T00:17:53+0100","text":"This discussion of &#039;glowing people&#039; made me think of bioluminescence, a chemical reaction between a light-emitting molecule (a luciferin) and an enzyme (a luciferase) in the required presence of oxygen. Luciferin is oxidized and luciferase catalyses the oxidation thus producing light (a luciferin-luciferase reaction), at least until all the luciferin is consumed. Both of the names <i>luciferin</i> and <i>luciferase</i> were created by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rapha%C3%ABl_Dubois\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">Raphaël Dubois</a> (1849-1929) from the Latin word <i>lucifer</i>, &#039;light-bearer&#039; (<i>lux</i>- &#039;light&#039;, <i>ferre</i>- &#039;to bring/to carry&#039;), which takes me to <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/2010/05/18/the-wave-chapter-23-lucifer-and-the-pot-of-gold-or-the-quest-for-the-holy-grail-of-no-anticipation/\" class=\"link link--internal\">Wave, chapter 23</a>.<br /><br />An example from an article in this <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/ketogenic-diet-powerful-dietary-strategy-for-certain-conditions.28799/post-362564\" class=\"link link--internal\">post</a>:<br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">The assay uses firefly luciferase in the presence of ATP, which oxidizes D-luciferin resulting in the emission of light.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":13215,"user":"ApotheosisMMC.","date":"2024-03-29T05:11:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":47,"user":"Ryan","date":"2024-03-24T06:29:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:47:41+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19148,"user":"Happy Poo","date":"2024-01-28T23:42:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":91,"user":"1984","date":"2024-01-28T19:27:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4180,"user":"Lilou","date":"2024-01-28T04:37:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:22:22+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:25:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-24T16:33:49+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11262,"user":"Matai","date":"2024-01-24T10:23:27+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":1533,"user":"Debra","date":"2024-01-23T21:03:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-23T19:57:39+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":12829,"user":"ryu","date":"2024-01-23T19:19:59+01