div></blockquote><br /><br />To begin to imagine this organic structure that is still unknown, the following analogy comes to mind:<br /><br />Suppose we are scientists, and using our physical senses, which they say are five, we observe and study the body, seeking to know all the things that exist in it.<br /><br />Now, let us think that this body is a huge area of countryside, with meadows, forests, bushes, etc.<br /><br />It is very feasible that we could be very close to a road, but as it is in disuse, no one travels on it, no cars, no trucks, or anything that we can hear, it is very easy not to know of the existence of this road, (&quot;Organic structure that transports throughout the body a fluid other than blood or lymph that is related to light&quot;).<br /><br />I am thinking that this truncated flow, is the activity that was taking place in the part of the DNA that was interrupted by 4D STS.<br />I strongly suspect this, because that&#039;s what they used light for.<br />And, the fluid is related to light.<br /><br />So, they may have used a type of light frequency, which when combined with that of the flow, acts exactly like a poison.<br /><br />Of course, all this has to be translated into &quot;information movement&quot;, so to speak.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":13215,"user":"ApotheosisMMC.","date":"2024-03-29T05:13:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:49:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-29T22:30:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:24:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-01-25T00:55:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:26:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-24T16:35:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-01-24T04:15:02+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-23T22:43:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7840,"user":"Stoneboss","date":"2024-01-23T21:12:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-23T19:57:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15985,"user":"Blaza","date":"2024-01-23T19:20:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14284,"user":"iamthatis","date":"2024-01-23T19:00:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19656,"user":"JandI","date":"2024-01-23T18:46:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-23T17:56:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":6460,"user":"Puma","date":"2024-01-23T17:00:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-23T16:14:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10630,"user":"JeanneT","date":"2024-01-23T14:59:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-01-23T13:45:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-23T12:10:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-01-23T11:56:25+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-01-23T09:14:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-01-23T07:37:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":360,"user":"mabar","date":"2024-01-23T07:06:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-23T06:50:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-01-23T06:43:12+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":7948,"user":"irjO","id":1157490,"date":"2024-01-23T07:25:58+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 17\" data-quote=\"Laura\" data-source=\"post: 1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1155572\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1155572\">Laura said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Q: (irjO) In a previous session, the C’s answered &quot;close&quot; when I asked if Teotihuacan was built by the Olmecs. What would make it closer, or what detail is missing? Who built it?<br /><br />A: Group you wouldn&#039;t recognize even if named. The previous answer is as close as you can get.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />There could be a big chance that the same group Cs mentioned, is the same group who originally built the pyramid of Cholula, see:<br /><br /><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Pyramid_of_Cholula?wprov=sfti1#Building_F\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">The great Cholula Pyramid </a><br /><br />Which is the largest pyramid found so far in the world. Like the city of Teotihuacan, nobody knows who really built it, and the oldest area inside the pyramid is dated even older than Teotihuacan. This could have been built around 6000 - 5000 BC, or perhaps by direct descendants of the Atlanteans, the same as the Sphinx, since the original pyramid was dedicated to Quetzalcoatl which is a serpent deity. And perhaps could be this ‘reptilian being’ who lived among humans in Atlantis for 1000 years. <br /><br />However, we got a little bit more of a hint from ancient Aztec legends about this forgotten group, and the Aztec legends said that the pyramid of Cholula was built by giants, the legends named this group the ‘Quinametzin Giants’<br /><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">As written in the book <b><i>El Mundo Mágico de los Dioses del Anáhuac</i></b> authored by Otilia Meza, a Quinametzin Giant stood more than 10 feet tall with a weight of around 600 pounds.<br /><br />As many other mythologies around the globe that mention the existence of giants, the Quinametzin too were by the gods because they did not venerate them, and their peak-civilization came to an end as a result of great calamities and as a punishment from the heavens for grave sins they had committed.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>From: <a href=\"https://www.ancient-code.com/the-quinametzin-giants-of-aztec-mythology-builders-of-the-pyramid-of-cholula-and-teotihuacan/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\">The Quinametzin Giants Of Aztec Mythology—Builders of The Pyramid Of Cholula And Teotihuacan</a><br /><br />Aztec legends said that they were the first raze who lived in the Mexico area, and the gods killed the majority of them through some cataclysmic events and a a huge flood (younger dryas event possibly?) which if that’s the case, then could be even older, around 8000 ish years BC <br />Now, Cs mention that it was a group that we wouldn’t known if named, so could be a similar group, or perhaps this was the group they referred to but were known by a different name. They said the Olmecs was ‘as close as we can get’, and legends says that the Olmecs came after and were enemies of this group. Perhaps the latter were the victorious group, and since they had also the knowledge of building megalithic structures, I suspect they were the ones who finalized and remodeled Teotihuacan which already existed as it is known today. Or at least the ruins that are known today.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":47,"user":"Ryan","date":"2024-03-24T06:32:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-01-31T20:51:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17284,"user":"ELT","date":"2024-01-3