rogen water devices</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>I’m and say I “ know” about it, but I am experimenting with it. My massage therapist who has very low white blood cell count and suffers from fatigue amongst other things, said she tried the tablets (mercola and others sell them) and said she had less fatigue and felt better.<br />so I decided to look i to it. Instead of buying the tablets I ended buying a water bottle that makes it, so no cost of buying the tablets every month, just have to replace the base (which makes the hydrogen) every 12-18 months.<br /><br />there are plenty of cheap bottles on eBay/amazon etc. it I decided to go with a more expensive one that is made here in Australia. I was going to to wait for a month to post about it here to see what benefits or not it has.<br /><br />ive had it about a week or two, and I have noticed a difference, less fatigue and more clarity of mind. However this could be a placebo, or maybe it’s just because I am drinking more water over all..  so fwiw if you’re curious I’d say give it a go…<br /><br />i would also say, if you have not already, get a shower filter, bathing in crappy water every day is just as bad as drinking poor water imo … just my 2 cents ..","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":47,"user":"Ryan","date":"2024-03-24T06:34:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-02-02T17:47:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3726,"user":"3DStudent","date":"2024-01-31T18:57:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-30T22:04:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4180,"user":"Lilou","date":"2024-01-29T14:51:34+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-01-28T06:42:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5809,"user":"Breo","date":"2024-01-27T20:59:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-