div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \"><span style=\"font-size: 15px\"><a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/session-13-january-2024.54173/post-1157808\" class=\"link link--internal\">#340</a> This isn&#039;t always the case in Native cultures. [...]</span></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>I know what you&#039;re talking about. And I know some examples of cruelty and strange social structure in certain tribes. I do not consider ancient people and their way of life ideal. When I talk about Indians, I generalize a little and select the phenomena I talk about.<br /><br />My interest is aimed at finding the “natural” and “instilled” characteristics of a person. Or the characteristics of his worldview. And I understand perfectly well that in different circumstances people behave in diametrically opposite ways.<br /><br />And it turns out that even Cassiopeia suggests that pre-agrarian societies had some special characteristics. Something valuable that we have lost. This is an important additional pointer for me.<br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \"><span style=\"font-size: 9px\">Google Translate:<br />Я в курсе, о чём вы говорите. И знаю некоторые примеры жестокости и странного общественного устройства в отдельных племенах. Я не считаю древних людей и их образ жизни идеальными. Когда я говорю об индейцах, я немного обобщаю и отбираю явления, о которых говорю. // Мой интерес направлен на поиск &quot;естественных&quot; и &quot;привитых&quot; характеристик человека. Или характеристик его мировоззрения. И я прекрасно понимаю, что в разных обстоятельствах люди ведут себя диаметрально противоположным образом. // И получается так, что даже Кассиопея подсказывает, что доаграрные общества имели некоторые особенные характеристики. Что-то ценное, что мы потеряли. Это для меня важный дополнительный указатель.</span></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-01-30T22:12:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-01-28T07:56:48+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-01-27T16:05:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-01-27T09:39:24+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":118,"user":"annp","date":"2024-01-27T02:17:06+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-01-25T23:10:01+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2292,"user":"Aeneas","date":"2024-01-25T19:53:05+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-01-25T16:27:06+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18380,"user":"Alix","date":"2024-01-25T13:40:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-25T13:36:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-01-25T12:14:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-01-25T12:02:25+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-25T08:24:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-01-25T02:30:37+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":27,"user":"Beau","date":"2024-01-25T02:01:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-01-25T01:44:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-01-25T01:23:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10829,"user":"Jtucker","date":"2024-01-25T01:11:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-01-25T00:36:02+0100","