en to give to others what you yourself has been lacking. I remember vaguely a quote from an earlier session that this was perhaps the best form of giving one could aspire to, to give to those what you yourself have not. And I know I have a long way to go. But in lack of knowing how to &quot;give back&quot; fully I find myself grasping for something, no matter how small, otherwise I fall into the trap of taking; consuming. Giving nothing in return. <br /><br />Thank you again to Laura and Andromeda and all others who continue to pour into this investment. Really, truly, thank you. It means more than you know, and more than I may ever be able to express or repay, and I&#039;m working on this.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":9854,"user":"oli 518","date":"2024-02-26T01:08:16+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":3936,"user":"Andrian","date":"2024-02-07T18:08:54+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2381,"user":"kinyash","date":"2024-02-05T05:37:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-04T12:52:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-02-03T21:11:47+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7509,"user":"candasiri","date":"2024-02-02T10:01:27+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15102,"user":"Kari Baba","date":"2024-02-01T17:11:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7597,"user":"hiker","date":"2024-02-01T06:08:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17281,"user":"Aylen","date":"2024-02-01T00:04:28+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17637,"user":"MikeCopp","date":"2024-01-31T16:41:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17284,"user":"ELT","date":"2024-01-31T14:25:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-31T12:09:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3140,"user":"Bluefyre","date":"2024-01-30T22:15:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-01-30T12:49:01+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-30T0