ckquote><br />Hi Pearce. I&#039;m glad to hear that you feel the need to help in any way you can to help others. <br />I just want to tell you not to let the anxiety of doing that get the better of you.<br />It is true that doing a practical task, or activity that is tangible or identifiable to others, and easily recognizable as a service, is a good and important thing to do, for a variety of reasons.<br />However, that is not the only important thing.<br />It is always good to remember that by the mere fact of applying the knowledge acquired so far, we are already helping those around us and ourselves. <br />Applying &quot;external consideration&quot; in our interactions, for example, has an enormous impact on our environment and therefore on the world.<br />I don&#039;t know if what I am saying will help you to reduce your worries, but I wish it would. <br />I know the feelings you are going through, and at least in my case, reflecting and/or thinking in that direction, has helped me a lot to slow down, adapting little by little to the rhythm of the Soul.  <br />As far as I can see you are doing very well, because you are cautious and have asked for guidance regarding Reiki, which is a very delicate matter. Surely others here will help you with that information. <br />Good luck with that.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-04T12:53:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-02-03T21:12:29+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-01-31T12:42:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-01-30T12:50:16+0100","reaction":"Love"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-01-30T06:52:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5809,"user":"Breo","date":"2024-01-29T22:11:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15669,"user":"Henchman 21","date":"2024-01-29T19:02:46+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18714,"user":"Freya Stewart","da