t&#039;s more like, say, a <b>4th density fluid</b>?<br />A: <b>Yes</b><br /><br />Q: (L) And the structure itself is fourth density when it exists in the body?<br />A: Yes<br /><br />Q: (L) And we have the potential for this if the DNA were to be upregulated?<br />A: Yes</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />Very insightfull the unfolded question. That reminds a passage seen into the channeling group of <b><i>Ra, Law of One</i>:</b><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \"><i>Tilting at Windmills</i>, Carla Rueckert &amp; McCarty<br /><br />..........................<br />GARY: What is initiation? And how, in general, may the seeker skillfully navigate an initiation?<br />JIM: Hmm, that’s a really good question. Don was undergoing initiation at his death. Initiation usually involves some type of a challenge. It’s an opportunity to become more available to power, you might say, more available to evolution and to the ability to expand your own consciousness. There’s usually some sort of a test, some sort of a challenge that you’ve got to overcome or to meet—to answer the questions, solve the riddles, solve the puzzles—and it usually involves a good deal of effort.<br /><br />Other than that general description there are apparently all kinds of initiations. One that Don asked about was—he was talking to Ra about an incident many years in the past when <b>his arm began to glow during meditation. </b>As he moved it up and down, there was a <b>blue glow</b> to it.<br /><br />CARLA: He was getting this encouragement to move his arm on the top of a chair—the chair’s arm—up and down very quickly [makes a swishing sound] like that. It began to glow blue, and he looked at that and watched his arm and he asked the fellow he was meditating with, whose name was Frank, he said, “Frank, do you see this?” Frank said, “You’re going blue!” and Don said, “Frank, I’m sure glad you can see that.” [laughs]<br />.................................<br /><br /><i>Ra, Law of One</i><br /><br />Q: <b>In meditation</b> a number of years ago my <b>arm</b> started to <b>glow</b>, moving rapidly involuntarily. What was that?<br />RA: The phenomenon was an analogy made available to you from your <b>higher self.</b> The analogy was that the being that you were was living in a way not understood by, shall we say, physicists, scientists, or doctors.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote></div>","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-02-07T17:52:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2556,"user":"clerck de bonk","date":"2024-02-06T12:30:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-02-04T21:11:25+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5393,"user":"sbeaudry","date":"2024-02-04T19:14:31+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":2567,"user":"miguel angel","date":"2024-02-04T12:42:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":12854,"user":"Tuulikki","date":"2024-02-04T10:32:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3863,"user":"findit","date":"2024-02-03T21:26:20+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":882,"user":"latulipenoire","date":"2024-02-03T03:31:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4180,"user":"Lilou","date":"2024-02-02T20:59:00+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":3,"user":"Approaching Infinity","date":"2024-02-02T17:03:56+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18747,"user":"Myeong In","date":"2024-02-02T13:08:22+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-02-02T05:07:08+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-02-01T23:59:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id"