ser":"happyliza","date":"2024-02-07T18:22:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15102,"user":"Kari Baba","date":"2024-02-07T13:31:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15332,"user":"Matty F","date":"2024-02-06T13:14:14+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-02-06T11:26:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19656,"user":"JandI","date":"2024-02-05T20:26:32+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-02-05T18:36:33+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-02-05T14:29:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-02-05T10:00:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-02-05T05:55:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14284,"user":"iamthatis","date":"2024-02-05T02:49:50+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-02-05T01:41:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11429,"user":"trytofly","date":"2024-02-04T23:44:31+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-02-04T23:36:44+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":15533,"user":"Deliverance","date":"2024-02-04T22:29:51+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-02-04T22:11:23+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-02-04T21:15:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-02-04T20:19:18+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-02-04T20:07:12+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":19234,"user":"ericw33","id":1160076,"date":"2024-02-04T21:36:52+0100","text":"This may or may-not be related to the light emanations as the C&#039;s describe but about 20-years ago a friend on speakerphone and I were doing some experiments.  Mostly on that day along the lines of programing water using guided meditation (just ideas I had).<br /><br />Anyways I did a &#039;power-up&#039; which is like moving to another location (non-physical).  There&#039;s not much there (ie: no buildings, trees, grass..) but it has 3/three distinct attributes.<br /><br />1. BRIGHT.  R<u>eally</u>, <u>really</u> bright (even though it&#039;s not physical, this was outside my physical body).  It&#039;s either white or golden/yellowish-white.<br />2. HOT. The heat was due to the intense &#039;vibration&#039; (hard to explain).  It was really nice - like after being 1/2 frozen in winter and finding a hot-tub.  When I say &#039;vibration&#039; I mean, really, really high and not like &#039;here&#039;.<br />3. MENTAL.  Not crazy-mental, but, I just mean whatever you think manifests.  It&#039; very tiring as there is no delay so you can&#039;t really have an internal thought process going on (which I didn&#039;t like).  <br /><br />Once back I was &#039;glowing&#039; for a period of time and I could also make limbs glow white as I wanted afterwards.  Now it&#039;s hard to stay inside you body so I had to ground later on but I did try an un-announced experiment with my friend (whom was still on the speakerphone) and it did work so it wasn&#039;t just my imagination.<br /><br />They haven&#039;t described 4D as super-bright and hot (due to vibrations) so it&#039;s <u>not</u> 4D but the after-effects may be along the lines of what they were talking about.  It&#039;s probably something else, but, thought I would do a post just in case.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-02-12T04:19:59+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-02-11T19:24:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-02-07T18:24:22+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18714,"user":"Freya Stewart","date":"2024-02-07T17:40:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-02-06T05:08:25+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":19656,"user":"JandI","date":"2024-02-05T20:28:19+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-02-05T20:06:56+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-02-05T14:31:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-02-05T10:27:35+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-02-05T09:52:26+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-02-04T23:38:34+0100","reaction":"Wow"},{"user_id":15533,"user":"Deliverance","date":"2024-02-04T22:32:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-02-04T22:11:55+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":17284,"user":"ELT","id":1160192,"date":"2024-02-05T18:09:26+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 14284\" data-quote=\"iamthatis\" data-source=\"post: 1159595\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-title\"><a href=\"/forum/goto/post?id=1159595\"class=\"bbCodeBlock-sourceJump\"rel=\"nofollow\"data-xf-click=\"attribution\"data-content-selector=\"#post-1159595\">iamthatis said:</a></div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">Yeah, good point. We could say that the specific arrangement of the molecules in the water is what can make it special or &#039;holy&#039;. It mostly exists as a potential, or a sort of goddess-in-waiting, but can be actuated or structured by sound - song, prayer, the human voice.<br /><br />A protein has to be folded correctly (or shaped properly) to perform its task, and it could be that a song must be sung correctly (or shaped properly) in order to truly tap into water&#039;s potential, and open up the conduit for blessing, healing, protection, or whatever is being asked for to flow through.<br /><br />So there&#039;s a sort of required &#039;geometry of sound&#039; for making successful healing water. It&#039;s likely that any song, prayer, and good intention will be of benefit. However, In many Native American traditions there are specific water songs that must be sung correctly and in harmony in order to produce the desired effects. Lots of different water songs can be found on YouTube. Maybe these songs are an echo of what the ancients knew, some technology of song using water that might be similar to the technology of the singing stones that provided all that was required for life?<br /><br />The C&#039;s have mentioned karaoke and singing a number of times. There is a certain way of doing it with proper intent and preparation that can be beneficial, even hyperdimensional - and also a certain way in which it&#039;s more 3D and just for kicks:<br /><br />July 4, 2020:<br /><br /><br /><br />The sense I get from the Native American material that I&#039;ve studied is that the right songs must be sung in the right way, in the right &#039;key&#039; - the right tone or pitch. This word &#039;key&#039; is not just a material-plane musical term, but also references a sort of hyperdimensional &#039;key&#039; that opens up a &#039;door&#039; or a portal for blessings to come through.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />Indeed, there&#039;s also the possible implication of the megalithic technology in making the water heavy. Cs said people have been zapped at stonehenge.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">Session 9 Nov. 1994:</span><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \"><b>A:</b> Energy collector translevel; stonehenge was one. Stonehenge is a coil. The missing stones form a coil arrangement. People have been &quot;zapped&quot; at stonehenge.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote><br />Sound (singing or maybe music too?), movement (dance, spinning...?) and/or other vibration tools (tunning fork?) could be in the recipe to make stones do what they had to.  That is they would place themselves in the proper way, to then amplify and transduce higher level energies/voices, &#039;singing&#039; back. <br />This could bring the correct modification to make body water heavy... and ZAP !<br /><br />I also recall Leedskalnin was said to do his stone levitation deeds by night, soundless.<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">Session 23 Oct. 1999:</span><br /><blockquote data-attributes=\"\" data-quote=\"\" data-source=\"\"class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \"><b>Q:</b> (A) How was he producing these sound waves?<br /><br /><b>A:</b> Through correlation of rocks and power source, obtained &quot;illegally.&quot; Instrument was similar to a tuning fork, but energized to a level that was lethal if one were to come in contact with it, or its ground.</div><div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">Click to expand...</a></div></div></blockquote>Could sound frequency for levitation be different than for water composition change, if singing is involved in the latter ?<br /><br />I also wondered about the relation to spiritual advancement. As the <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/threads/session-13-january-2024.54173/post-1157192\" class=\"link link--internal\">alchemical prima materia is water</a>, as Cs said, then the achievement of the Great Work would be the transmutation to heavy water.<br />So, would an enough spiritual advancement through Work on Self allow to develop a state of mind/being, in which a particular sound could be produced which, coupled with stones use, would zap us to 4D ...?<br />Did Fulcanelli use stones ?<br /><br />That&#039;s many questions... I wish I&#039;ll know the answers at some point.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":17775,"user":"OpenMindOpenHeart","date":"2024-03-03T01:52:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11403,"user":"Sylvia","date":"2024-02-12T04:20:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-02-11T19:30:04+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-02-09T13:50:39+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7505,"user":"MK Scarlett","date":"2024-02-07T19:53:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-02-07T18:26:45+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":4527,"user":"Talas","date":"2024-02-07T14:04:06+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":9839,"user":"Jo Bugman","date":"2024-02-07T02:28:59+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16791,"user":"Benjamin","date":"2024-02-07T00:04:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":13630,"user":"Stella Marys","date":"2024-02-06T16:07:09+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":203,"user":"thorbiorn","date":"2024-02-06T12:22:20+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":7284,"user":"Don Cesar","date":"2024-02-06T11:28:17+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17865,"user":"Anizta","date":"2024-02-06T05:08:57+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17316,"user":"KaWaiAwaAwa","date":"2024-02-05T23:38:43+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-02-05T21:53:15+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-02-05T21:05:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-02-05T20:08:03+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5546,"user":"Thebull","date":"2024-02-05T19:23:58+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-02-05T19:01:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":14284,"user":"iamthatis","date":"2024-02-05T18:18:03+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":17284,"user":"ELT","id":1160196,"date":"2024-02-05T18:23:16+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attributes=\"member: 672\" data-quote=\"mkrnhr\" data