ot to Day 3... About the amount of water - plenty! The zeolite needs to be flushed properly. It has an excellent ability to absorb whatever is in the intestines, but it&#039;s not supposed to be staying there. So don&#039;t be stingy on the water! <br /><br />If I was to do another cure today, I&#039;d start out with a tiny amount of zeolite, and lots of water through-out the day. All in all, follow the advice of iyan above.<br /><br />I did a <a href=\"https://cassiopaea.org/forum/search/531538/?q=zeolite&amp;o=date\" class=\"link link--internal\">search for &quot;zeolite&quot;</a> in the forum and there seems to be bits of info here and there, so do try to see if you can find more info that might come in handy. <img src=\"/forum/styles/cass/smilies/thumbup.gif\"  class=\"smilie\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\":thup:\" title=\"Thumbs up    :thup:\" data-shortname=\":thup:\" />","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":18632,"user":"Bernardo GA","date":"2024-02-11T17:49:40+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18714,"user":"Freya Stewart","date":"2024-02-11T14:32:21+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":5223,"user":"happyliza","date":"2024-02-11T14:05:55+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11705,"user":"Tuatha de Danaan","date":"2024-02-09T20:31:10+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":10595,"user":"Korzik18","date":"2024-02-09T19:12:12+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11897,"user":"PERLOU","date":"2024-02-09T18:43:07+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-02-09T14:08:38+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":18193,"user":"wilfried","date":"2024-02-09T11:02:30+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":635,"user":"flashgordonv","date":"2024-02-09T00:24:36+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":16918,"user":"XPan","date":"2024-02-08T22:30:42+0100","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":11699,"user":"Kay Kim","date":"2024-02-08T22:07:25+0100","reaction":"Like"}]},{"user_id":4487,"user":"iyan","id":1160784,"date":"2024-02-09T00:05:54+0100","text":"<blockquote data-attri