ip compartments and / or same [Lizzie-]purpose rooms on the surface. When they felt they are convenient in human-worshiped cities. I think a clear sign of these physical abduction-memories would be a slowly welling up panic = PTSD, from the past.","attachments":[],"reactions":[{"user_id":19544,"user":"meadow_wind","date":"2024-08-10T15:22:18+0200","reaction":"Like"},{"user_id":17945,"user":"Claus","date":"2024-07-31T14:26:00+0200","reaction":"Like"}]}]}
